#   * dqlite/go-dqlite — Canonical's distributed SQLite Go bindings
#   * rqlite/gorqlite — Go client for rqlite (not direct SQLite)
#
# mattn/go-sqlite3 is the chosen Axis-27 Go closer because:
#   - It is the dominant Go SQLite binding by deployment + tooling
#   - It implements the database/sql interface
#   - marmot specifically uses mattn/go-sqlite3 for its embedded
#     storage layer
#   - It demonstrates the cgo-bridged SQLite C library access pattern
#     that mirrors Rust's rusqlite (which also wraps the C library
#     via bindgen)
